{"id": 6845, "title": "Ticket #6845: Remove ALLOW_VM_CRUFT", "description": "<blockquote>\nIn the old days of condor, we called slots VMs, and a bunch of slot-related knobs had the phrase \"VM\" in them.  When virtual machine technology became big, this got really confusing, so we renamed VMs to be \"slots\".  For backward compatibility, we added a knob \"ALLOW_VM_CRUFT\" to keep these old knobs and old names.  It has been off for at least a decade.  Now is the time to remove this cruft.</blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2019-Jan-04 09:20</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/012fbe6974a000761217206eca87148551fee547\">[55941]</a></span>: (<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=6845\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('6845'); return false;\" title=\"Remove ALLOW_VM_CRUFT\">#6845</a></span>) Removed associated ALLOW_VM_CRUFT documentation  (By Tim Theisen )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2018-Dec-20 16:05</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/962fd3d2e091781bad9552828d6ac496764a44ee\">[55922]</a></span>: Remove ALLOW_VM_CRUFT <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=6845\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('6845'); return false;\" title=\"Remove ALLOW_VM_CRUFT\">#6845</a></span>  (By Greg Thain )</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>", "type": "enhance